          "_name": "people01",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"people01\" group=\"People\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"8\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Title\" name=\"showmainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Text\" name=\"showmainText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Buttons\" name=\"showmainButtons\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showsubTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/whatsapp-image-2026-03-15-at-9.34.10-pm.webp\" parallax selected>\n    </fieldset>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n      <div class=\"col-lg-5 mb-5\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-maintitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-maintitle\" mbr-if=\"showmainTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>About Us</b></h3>\n        <p class=\"mbr-section-maintext mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-maintext, .btn-move\" mbr-if=\"showmainText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">At Vibrant Hope Care Foundation, we believe that every life—no matter how vulnerable—deserves dignity, opportunity, and hope. Founded with a mission to uplift underserved children, families, and communities across Nigeria, our work is rooted in compassion, accountability, and sustainable impact.\n<br>\n<br>We serve over 250 children and youth across 5 local communities, providing daily meals, access to education, healthcare support, and emotional care. Our programs include literacy and vocational training, mobile health outreach, and community development projects such as clean water access and solar-powered learning hubs. In 2025 alone, we distributed over 12,000 meals, enrolled 85 children in school, and facilitated medical care for 300+ beneficiaries through our mobile clinics.\n<br>\n<br>Our foundation is fully registered and compliant with Nigeria’s NGO regulations, and we are actively aligning with the&nbsp; UK Charity Commission’s Public Benefit framework —ensuring our services are accessible, inclusive, and transparently managed.&nbsp;<br>\nWe are proud to a open Heart + a willing partnership/sponsors both local and international.&nbsp;<br><br>Every donation, every volunteer hour, and every partnership fuels our mission to build a future where hope rises—not just for one child, but for generations.<br>\n        </p>\n\n        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn btn-move\" mbr-if=\"showmainButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><strong>Read\n              more</strong></a></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"col-lg-7\">\n        <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n              <div class=\"col-md-7\">\n                <div class=\"align-left\">\n                  <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Our Mission</b></h3>\n                  <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showsubTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Our mission is to transform lives through faith-driven social action by supporting vulnerable communities, empowering individuals with sustainable opportunities, and providing compassionate care where it is needed most.</h4>\n                  <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Our mission is to transform lives through faith-driven social action by supporting vulnerable communities, empowering individuals with sustainable opportunities, and providing compassionate care where it is needed most.<br>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-right\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary-outline\" href=\"Impact-Reports.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><strong>Read\n                      more</strong></a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n              <div class=\"col-md-7\">\n                <div class=\"align-left\">\n                  <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Our Vision</b></h3>\n                  <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showsubTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Our Works</h4>\n                  <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">We envision communities where vulnerable individuals are supported with dignity, practical resources, and opportunities that enable them to build stable and hopeful futures.</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-right\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary-outline\" href=\"Governance-Accountability.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><strong>Read\n                      more</strong></a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item features-without-image\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n              <div class=\"col-md-7\">\n                <div class=\"align-left\">\n                  <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Our Public Benefit Commitment</b></h3>\n                  <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showsubTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Workshops</h4>\n                  <p class=\"mbr-section-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-text\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Vibrant Hope Care Foundation operates for the public benefit by addressing poverty, social isolation, and lack of access to essential resources in both the United Kingdom and Nigeria.<br><br>Our work is guided by three key areas of impact.<br>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"col-md-5\">\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-right\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-secondary-outline\" href=\"TheProjectPages.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><strong>Read\n                      more</strong></a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vdElzICYtE",
          "_anchor": "people01-v",
