          "_name": "timeline02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"timeline02\" group=\"News\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" value=\"6\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">Empowerment&nbsp;</h2>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><i>Vibrant Hope Care Foundation\n</i><div><i><u>Empowering Maternal Health, Widows and Orphans, Elderly and Sick in Nigeria</u></i></div></h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image active\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>The Empowerment&nbsp;Wing</b></p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Skills Acquisition for Widows and Orphans&nbsp;</b></h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>The Challenge<br></b><br>Widows and vulnerable individuals often face economic exclusion, limited job opportunities, and financial instability.&nbsp;<br></p><p><b>Our Response\n</b><br>Our Empowerment Wing provides practical training and tools that allow individuals to build sustainable livelihoods.&nbsp;<br></p><p><b>Training programs include:\n<br></b>Tailoring and fashion design\n<br>Sustainable agriculture\n<br>Digital literacy and small business skills\n<br>Participants also receive starter tools to begin their own micro-enterprises.</p><p><b>Impact Goal\n</b><br>Help participants transition from financial dependency to independent income generation.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/whatsapp-image-2026-03-17-at-2.59.16-pm.webp\" alt data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>The Empowerment&nbsp;Wing</b></p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Skills Acquisition for Widows and Orphans&nbsp;</b></h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>The Challenge<br></b><br>Widows and vulnerable individuals often face economic exclusion, limited job opportunities, and financial instability.&nbsp;<br></p><p><b>Our Response\n</b><br>Our Empowerment Wing provides practical training and tools that allow individuals to build sustainable livelihoods.&nbsp;<br></p><p><b>Training programs include:\n<br></b>Tailoring and fashion design\n<br>Sustainable agriculture\n<br>Digital literacy and small business skills\n<br>Participants also receive starter tools to begin their own micro-enterprises.</p><p><b>Impact Goal\n</b><br>Help participants transition from financial dependency to independent income generation.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/whatsapp-image-2026-03-15-at-9.36.49-pm.webp\" alt data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "timeline02-24",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vdKA6JPqDq",
